{"tid":1464210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以輕鬆愉快嘅方式，去記錄香港警察辛勞的一天！","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:48:48.000Z","uid":163839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6b84728ff1dab12951959d19a1f14effc8e280fe","tid":1464210,"uid":163839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:36:46.000Z","msg":"我地一齊支持下呢個插畫家好無呀 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>@hyuenbb</strong>: 警察唔易做</span> <br />\n佢個illustration ig: <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>@hk_police</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oP4YQaZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoP4YQaZ.jpg&h=4b89c133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>靚女d就鬧我係🐔 香港大把女明星都靚女la 話我似大陸網紅 都幾搞笑嘅 不過都多謝你哋承認我靚女 大陸網紅都幾有錢，唔洗加班之後有機會我會試下做網紅 thanks <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">#hkpolice #香港警察</span> <span style=\"color: gold;\">#遊行 #反送中</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">#撐警察</span> #hkgirl </strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KXzmNXQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKXzmNXQ.jpg&h=8dfe0957&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UwfEzCR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUwfEzCR.jpg&h=4096c999&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲上過成報添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iFxrY42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiFxrY42.jpg&h=1f61fea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋應該效法佢支持警察嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jyUBBUc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjyUBBUc.jpg&h=e0276ec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JS0Uozf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJS0Uozf.jpg&h=3c553ae5&s=